OL,3,CMan charged with murder as 27-year-old
OL,4,Cvictim named
OL,6,FA man has been charged in connection
OL,7,Fwith the murder of a woman in
OL,8,FLincolnshire.
OL,10,FOfficers received a report that a
OL,11,Fwoman had suffered serious injuries
OL,12,Fand was found unconscious at a
OL,13,Fproperty on Warwickshires Way in
OL,14,FHorncastle at 4.23pm on Thursday 2
OL,15,FApril. She died at the scene.
OL,17,FShe has now been named by police as 27-
OL,18,Fyear-old Khyali Jana Rahim Bad Shah.
OL,19,FHer family are being supported by
OL,20,Fofficers.
