OL,3,CMan charged with murder as 27-year-old
OL,4,Cvictim named
OL,6,FThirty-four-year-old Mohammad Raees
OL,7,FMohammad Rahim, of Warwickshires Way
OL,8,Fin Horncastle has been charged with
OL,9,Fmurder.
OL,11,FHe has been remanded to custody to
OL,12,Fappear at Lincoln Magistrates' Court
OL,13,Fon Monday 6 April.
